| Tool                     | Use                                |
| ------------------------ | ---------------------------------- |
| **Python**               | Main programming language          |
| `pandas`                 | Data handling (tables, CSVs)       |
| `scikit-learn`           | Machine learning (training models) |
| `matplotlib`             | Graphs and charts                  |
| `streamlit` *(optional)* | Simple user interface (web app)    |
